c: 53
v: 32
t: "Balia beikalilanga okhukhola ebionono ebikhongo nende akeshifwabi, halali orwonono orutiti titi, Toto Nyasaye wuwo obulesheli bwe nobuunji, Ye abamanyile muno, olwa yabaloonga okhurula khuliloba , nende ngamwali mutsinda tsia banyinenywe, kho muleelole tawe, Ye amanyile muno owamuria"